<h4>Hi Admin!</h4>

<p> A user named <strong> <%= @user.name %></strong> has requested for the cabpool having ID: <strong> <%= @cabpool %></strong>. Please check the application for more information.</p>


<h4>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</h4>

<p><strong><%= @user.name %> (<%= @user.email %>)</strong> has requested for a
  cabpool having ID: <strong> <%= @cabpool %></strong>. </p>

<p> <%= @user.name %> lives at:</p>
<p><%= @user.address %></p>

<p>If you approve, <%= @user.name %> will be added to your carpool, and a confirmation email will
  be sent to both <%= @user.name %>.

<p>What would you like to do?</p>

<p><%= link_to('Approve this request', approve_reject_handler_url(token: @digest, user: @user.id, cabpool: @cabpool, approve: true), target: '_blank') %> </p>

<p><%= link_to('Reject this request', approve_reject_handler_url(token: @digest, user: @user.id, cabpool: @cabpool, approve: false), target: '_blank') %></p>

<p>Thanks!</p>
<p>Danglay</p>
